-- Turkey's Arcelik to set up fridge factory in Thailand for $100 mln
-- 
-- Fri Dec 12, 2014 10:20AM EST
-- None



ISTANBUL, Dec 12 (Reuters) - Turkish white goods maker Arcelik <ARCLK.IS> said on Friday it would invest $100 million over three years to set up a refrigerator factory in Thailand.

Arcelik will establish a company in Thailand for production, sales and marketing, it said in a statement to the Istanbul Stock Exchange.